<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>NATERRA — Small Choice, Big Impact</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Fraunces:ital,opsz,wght@0,9..144,300;0,9..144,400;0,9..144,500;0,9..144,600;1,9..144,400&family=Work+Sans:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="s[...]
<style>
  :root{
    --cream:#F4F1E7;
    --paper:#FBF9F3;
    --sage:#7A8A63;
    --olive:#3F4A30;
    --deepolive:#2B341F;
    --gold:#C7A769;
    --ink:#28281F;
    --line:rgba(43,52,31,0.14);
  }
  *{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box;}
  html{scroll-behavior:smooth;}
  body{background:var(--cream);color:var(--ink);font-family:'Work Sans',sans-serif;line-height:1.6;overflow-x:hidden;}
  h1,h2,h3{font-family:'Fraunces',serif;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-0.01em;color:var(--deepolive);}
  a{color:inherit;text-decoration:none;}
  img{max-width:100%;display:block;}
  .wrap{max-width:1180px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 32px;}

  nav{position:fixed;top:0;left:0;right:0;z-index:50;background:rgba(244,241,231,0.86);backdrop-filter:blur(10px);border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);}
  nav .wrap{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;height:78px;}
  .brand{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;}
  .brand img{height:40px;width:40px;object-fit:contain;}
  .brand span{font-family:'Fraunces',serif;font-size:1.3rem;letter-spacing:0.03em;color:var(--deepolive);}
  nav ul{display:flex;gap:36px;list-style:none;}
  nav ul a{font-size:0.92rem;color:var(--olive);position:relative;padding:4px 0;}
  nav ul a::after{content:'';position:absolute;left:0;bottom:-2px;width:0;height:1.5px;background:var(--gold);transition:width .3s ease;}
  nav ul a:hover::after{width:100%;}
  .nav-cta{background:var(--deepolive);color:var(--paper)!important;padding:10px 20px;border-radius:2px;font-size:0.85rem;}
  @media (max-width:760px){ nav ul li:not(.nav-cta-li){display:none;} }

  .hero{position:relative;min-height:100vh;display:flex;align-items:center;padding-top:78px;overflow:hidden;}
  .hero-bg-arc{position:absolute;width:1400px;height:1400px;border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:50%;top:50%;left:50%;transform:translate(-50%,-46%);pointer-events:none;}
  .hero-bg-arc.two{width:1000px;height:1000px;border-color:rgba(122,138,99,0.18);}
  .hero .wrap{position:relative;z-index:2;display:grid;grid-template-columns:1.1fr 0.9fr;gap:60px;align-items:center;width:100%;}
  @media (max-width:880px){ .hero .wrap{grid-template-columns:1fr;text-align:center;gap:36px;} }

  .eyebrow{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;font-size:0.78rem;letter-spacing:0.16em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--sage);margin-bottom:22px;}
  .eyebrow::before{content:'';width:22px;height:1px;background:var(--gold);}
  @media (max-width:880px){ .eyebrow{justify-content:center;} .eyebrow::before{display:none;} }

  .hero h1{font-size:clamp(2.6rem,5.6vw,4.4rem);line-height:1.02;margin-bottom:22px;}
  .hero h1 em{font-style:italic;color:var(--sage);font-weight:400;}
  .hero p.lead{font-size:1.08rem;color:#4b5240;max-width:480px;margin-bottom:34px;}
  @media (max-width:880px){ .hero p.lead{margin:0 auto 34px;} }

  .btn-row{display:flex;gap:16px;flex-wrap:wrap;}
  @media (max-width:880px){ .btn-row{justify-content:center;} }
  .btn{display:inline-block;padding:14px 30px;border-radius:2px;font-size:0.92rem;letter-spacing:0.02em;transition:all .25s ease;}
  .btn.primary{background:var(--deepolive);color:var(--paper);}
  .btn.primary:hover{background:var(--olive);transform:translateY(-2px);}
  .btn.ghost{border:1px solid var(--olive);color:var(--deepolive);}
  .btn.ghost:hover{background:var(--olive);color:var(--paper);}

  .hero-logo-box{position:relative;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;}
  .hero-logo-box img{width:min(100%,360px);filter:drop-shadow(0 18px 40px rgba(43,52,31,0.18));animation:rise 1.4s ease both;}
  @keyframes rise{from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px);}to{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0);}}

  .scroll-cue{position:absolute;bottom:34px;left:50%;transform:translateX(-50%);font-size:0.72rem;letter-spacing:0.16em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--sage);display:flex;flex-direction:column;al[...]
  .scroll-cue .stem{width:1px;height:32px;background:linear-gradient(var(--sage),transparent);animation:grow 2.4s ease-in-out infinite;}
  @keyframes grow{0%,100%{height:14px;}50%{height:34px;}}

  section{padding:120px 0;position:relative;}
  .tag{font-size:0.78rem;letter-spacing:0.16em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--gold);margin-bottom:14px;display:block;}
  .section-head{max-width:640px;margin-bottom:64px;}
  .section-head.center{margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto;text-align:center;}
  .section-head h2{font-size:clamp(1.9rem,3.6vw,2.7rem);}
  .section-head p{color:#5a5f4d;margin-top:16px;font-size:1.02rem;}

  .root-divider{height:90px;position:relative;background:var(--cream);}
  .root-divider svg{position:absolute;top:0;left:50%;transform:translateX(-50%);width:100%;max-width:1180px;height:100%;}

  .about{background:var(--paper);}
  .about-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:0.9fr 1.1fr;gap:70px;align-items:start;}
  @media (max-width:880px){ .about-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr;} }
  .about-grid p{color:#494f3d;margin-bottom:18px;font-size:1.02rem;}
  .about-figures{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);gap:30px;margin-top:40px;}
  .figure h3{font-size:2.1rem;color:var(--sage);font-weight:500;}
  .figure span{font-size:0.84rem;color:#6b7059;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.08em;}

  /* PRODUCTS */
  .products{background:var(--cream);}
  .product-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:30px;}
  @media (max-width:880px){ .product-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr;} }
  .product-card{background:var(--paper);border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:6px;overflow:hidden;transition:transform .3s ease,box-shadow .3s ease;}
  .product-card:hover{transform:translateY(-6px);box-shadow:0 20px 40px rgba(43,52,31,0.1);}
  .product-thumb{aspect-ratio:1/1;background:linear-gradient(160deg,#E7E3D2,#D6D9C2);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;position:relative;}
  .product-thumb span.leaf{font-size:2.4rem;}
  .product-body{padding:26px 24px;}
  .product-body h3{font-size:1.2rem;margin-bottom:8px;}
  .product-body p{color:#5a5f4d;font-size:0.92rem;margin-bottom:16px;}
  .product-price{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;}
  .product-price strong{color:var(--deepolive);font-size:1.1rem;}
  .product-price a{font-size:0.85rem;color:var(--sage);border-bottom:1px solid var(--sage);}

  /* VALUES */
  .values{background:var(--paper);}
  .values-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:2px;background:var(--line);border:1px solid var(--line);}
  @media (max-width:880px){ .values-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr;} }
  .value-card{background:var(--cream);padding:48px 38px;transition:background .3s ease;}
  .value-card:hover{background:#FFFEFB;}
  .value-card .vnum{font-family:'Fraunces',serif;font-style:italic;color:var(--gold);font-size:1.1rem;margin-bottom:18px;display:block;}
  .value-card h3{font-size:1.3rem;margin-bottom:12px;}
  .value-card p{color:#5a5f4d;font-size:0.96rem;}

  /* PROCESS */
  .process{background:var(--deepolive);color:var(--cream);}
  .process h2,.process .tag{color:var(--cream);}
  .process .tag{color:var(--gold);}
  .process .section-head p{color:#C8CEB9;}
  .process-list{display:flex;flex-direction:column;}
  .process-row{display:grid;grid-template-columns:90px 1.4fr 1fr;gap:30px;align-items:center;padding:30px 0;border-top:1px solid rgba(244,241,231,0.14);}
  .process-row:last-child{border-bottom:1px solid rgba(244,241,231,0.14);}
  @media (max-width:760px){ .process-row{grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:10px;} }
  .process-row .pnum{font-family:'Fraunces',serif;font-style:italic;font-size:1.1rem;color:var(--gold);}
  .process-row h3{color:var(--cream);font-size:1.4rem;font-weight:500;}
  .process-row p{color:#B9C0A6;font-size:0.95rem;}

  /* TESTIMONI */
  .testi{background:var(--cream);}
  .testi-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:30px;}
  @media (max-width:880px){ .testi-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr;} }
  .testi-card{background:var(--paper);padding:34px 30px;border-radius:6px;border:1px solid var(--line);}
  .testi-card p{font-size:0.98rem;color:#494f3d;margin-bottom:18px;font-style:italic;font-family:'Fraunces',serif;}
  .testi-card .who{font-size:0.85rem;color:var(--sage);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.06em;}

  .impact{background:var(--paper);text-align:center;}
  .impact .wrap{max-width:760px;}
  .impact h2{font-size:clamp(2rem,4vw,2.8rem);margin-bottom:22px;}
  .impact p{color:#5a5f4d;font-size:1.05rem;margin-bottom:40px;}

  footer{background:var(--olive);color:#DCE0CC;padding:70px 0 36px;}
  .footer-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1.4fr 1fr 1fr;gap:50px;margin-bottom:50px;}
  @media (max-width:760px){ .footer-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:34px;} }
  .footer-brand{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;margin-bottom:16px;}
  .footer-brand img{height:34px;width:34px;}
  .footer-brand span{font-family:'Fraunces',serif;font-size:1.2rem;color:var(--paper);}
  footer p{color:#B9C0A6;font-size:0.92rem;max-width:300px;}
  footer h4{color:var(--paper);font-size:0.85rem;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:16px;font-weight:500;}
  footer ul{list-style:none;}
  footer li{margin-bottom:10px;font-size:0.92rem;color:#C7CDB4;}
  .footer-bottom{border-top:1px solid rgba(220,224,204,0.16);padding-top:26px;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:10px;font-size:0.82rem;color:#9CA386;}

  [data-reveal]{opacity:0;transform:translateY(22px);transition:opacity .7s ease,transform .7s ease;}
  [data-reveal].in{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0);}
  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce){*{animation:none!important;transition:none!important;}[data-reveal]{opacity:1;transform:none;}}
  a:focus-visible, button:focus-visible{outline:2px solid var(--gold);outline-offset:3px;}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<nav>
  <div class="wrap">
    <a class="brand" href="#top">
      <img src="data:image/jpeg;base64,/9j/4AAQSkZJRgABAQAAAQABAAD/2wCEAAYGBgYHBgcICAcKCwoLCg8ODAwODxYQERAREBYiFRkVFRkVIh4kHhweJB42KiYmKjY+NDI0PkxERExfWl98fKcBBgYGBgcGBwgIBwoLCgsKDw4MDA4PFhAREBEQFiIVG[...]
      <span>NATERRA</span>
    </a>
    <ul>
      <li><a href="#about">Tentang</a></li>
      <li><a href="#products">Produk</a></li>
      <li><a href="#values">Kenapa Kami</a></li>
      <li class="nav-cta-li"><a class="nav-cta" href="#order">Pesan Sekarang</a></li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</nav>

<header class="hero" id="top">
  <div class="hero-bg-arc"></div>
  <div class="hero-bg-arc two"></div>
  <div class="wrap">
    <div>
      <span class="eyebrow">Naterra — Tissue Ramah Lingkungan</span>
      <h1>Pilihan kecil,<br><em>dampak besar</em> bagi bumi.</h1>
      <p class="lead">Naterra adalah tisu lembut berbahan dasar ramah lingkungan untuk kebutuhan harianmu — dibuat dengan bahan yang lebih bertanggung jawab, tanpa mengurangi kenyamanan.</p>
      <div class="btn-row">
        <a class="btn primary" href="#order">Pesan via WhatsApp</a>
        <a class="btn ghost" href="#products">Lihat Produk</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-logo-box">
      <img src="data:image/jpeg;base64,/9j/4AAQSkZJRgABAQAAAQABAAD/2wCEAAYGBgYHBgcICAcKCwoLCg8ODAwODxYQERAREBYiFRkVFRkVIh4kHhweJB42KiYmKjY+NDI0PkxERExfWl98fKcBBgYGBgcGBwgIBwoLCgsKDw4MDA4PFhAREBEQFiIVG[...]
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="scroll-cue"><span>Gulir</span><span class="stem"></span></div>
</header>

<div class="root-divider">
  <svg viewBox="0 0 1180 90" preserveAspectRatio="none" fill="none">
    <path d="M0 0 L1180 0" stroke="#2B341F" stroke-opacity="0.12"/>
    <path d="M590 0 V20 C590 40 560 40 540 55 C520 68 500 68 480 80" stroke="#7A8A63" stroke-width="1.4"/>
    <path d="M590 20 C590 40 620 40 645 55 C665 68 690 68 712 82" stroke="#7A8A63" stroke-width="1.4"/>
    <path d="M590 30 C588 48 588 60 588 78" stroke="#C7A769" stroke-width="1.4"/>
  </svg>
</div>

<section class="about" id="about">
  <div class="wrap about-grid">
    <div data-reveal>
      <span class="tag">Tentang Naterra</span>
      <h2 style="font-size:clamp(1.9rem,3.6vw,2.6rem);">UMKM lokal, bahan pilihan, niat baik untuk bumi.</h2>
    </div>
    <div data-reveal>
      <p>Naterra dimulai dari dapur produksi kecil dengan satu prinsip: kebutuhan sehari-hari sekecil selembar tisu pun bisa jadi keputusan baik untuk bumi. Kami memilih bahan baku pulp bersertifikat [...]
      <p>Setiap kotak dan kemasan Naterra dirancang minim plastik, mudah didaur ulang, dan tetap menjaga kelembutan serta daya serap yang kamu butuhkan di rumah, kantor, maupun saat bepergian.</p>
      <div class="about-figures">
        <div class="figure"><h3>3.200+</h3><span>Pelanggan Setia</span></div>
        <div class="figure"><h3>15+</h3><span>Kota Terjangkau</span></div>
        <div class="figure"><h3>100%</h3><span>Bebas Pewangi Keras</span></div>
        <div class="figure"><h3>2022</h3><span>Tahun Berdiri</span></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="products" id="products">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="section-head" data-reveal>
      <span class="tag">Produk Kami</span>
      <h2>Tisu untuk setiap momen harianmu.</h2>
      <p>Lembut, kuat, dan dibuat dari bahan yang lebih ramah lingkungan — tersedia dalam beberapa varian sesuai kebutuhan.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="product-grid">
      <div class="product-card" data-reveal>
        <div class="product-thumb"><span class="leaf">🌿</span></div>
        <div class="product-body">
          <h3>Naterra Facial Tissue</h3>
          <p>Tisu wajah dua lapis, lembut di kulit, isi 250 lembar per kotak.</p>
          <div class="product-price"><strong>Rp14.000</strong><a href="#order">Pesan</a></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="product-card" data-reveal>
        <div class="product-thumb"><span class="leaf">🌱</span></div>
        <div class="product-body">
          <h3>Naterra Travel Pack</h3>
          <p>Kemasan saku praktis, cocok dibawa ke mana saja, isi 100 lembar.</p>
          <div class="product-price"><strong>Rp6.000</strong><a href="#order">Pesan</a></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="product-card" data-reveal>
        <div class="product-thumb"><span class="leaf">🍃</span></div>
        <div class="product-body">
          <h3>Naterra Kitchen Roll</h3>
          <p>Tisu dapur daya serap tinggi untuk kebutuhan rumah tangga harian.</p>
          <div class="product-price"><strong>Rp18.000</strong><a href="#order">Pesan</a></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="values" id="values">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="section-head" data-reveal>
      <span class="tag">Kenapa Naterra</span>
      <h2>Tiga akar yang menumbuhkan setiap kotak tisu.</h2>
      <p>Bukan cuma soal kelembutan — ini soal pilihan yang kamu buat setiap kali memakainya.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="values-grid">
    <div class="value-card" data-reveal>
      <span class="vnum">Akar</span>
      <h3>Bahan yang Bertanggung Jawab</h3>
      <p>Pulp bersertifikat dan proses produksi yang lebih hemat air serta energi.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="value-card" data-reveal>
      <span class="vnum">Tunas</span>
      <h3>Kemasan Minim Plastik</h3>
      <p>Kemasan dirancang agar lebih mudah didaur ulang dan ringan jejaknya di bumi.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="value-card" data-reveal>
      <span class="vnum">Naungan</span>
      <h3>Nyaman untuk Keluarga</h3>
      <p>Lembut di kulit, bebas pewangi keras, aman untuk pemakaian harian seluruh keluarga.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="process">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="section-head" data-reveal>
      <span class="tag">Cara Pesan</span>
      <h2>Tiga langkah, tisu sampai di depan pintu.</h2>
      <p>Pemesanan mudah lewat WhatsApp atau marketplace pilihanmu.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="process-list">
      <div class="process-row" data-reveal>
        <span class="pnum">01</span>
        <h3>Pilih Varian</h3>
        <p>Tentukan produk dan jumlah yang kamu butuhkan dari katalog kami.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="process-row" data-reveal>
        <span class="pnum">02</span>
        <h3>Konfirmasi Pesanan</h3>
        <p>Chat tim kami via WhatsApp untuk konfirmasi alamat dan pembayaran.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="process-row" data-reveal>
        <span class="pnum">03</span>
        <h3>Tisu Diantar</h3>
        <p>Pesanan dikemas rapi dan dikirim ke alamatmu lewat kurir pilihan.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="testi">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="section-head center" data-reveal>
      <span class="tag">Kata Pelanggan</span>
      <h2>Dipercaya rumah tangga seperti rumahmu.</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="testi-grid">
      <div class="testi-card" data-reveal>
        <p>"Lembut dan nggak gampang sobek, anak-anak juga suka pakai untuk lap tangan."</p>
        <span class="who">— Rina, Bandung</span>
      </div>
      <div class="testi-card" data-reveal>
        <p>"Suka karena kemasannya simpel, nggak banyak plastik. Tetap kuat dibawa ke tas."</p>
        <span class="who">— Dimas, Surabaya</span>
      </div>
      <div class="testi-card" data-reveal>
        <p>"Repeat order terus untuk kebutuhan dapur, daya serapnya bagus banget."</p>
        <span class="who">— Putri, Jakarta</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="impact" id="order">
  <div class="wrap" data-reveal>
    <span class="tag">Pesan Sekarang</span>
    <h2>Pilihan kecil hari ini, dampak besar untuk bumi esok hari.</h2>
    <p>Hubungi kami untuk pemesanan eceran, grosir, maupun kerja sama reseller.</p>
    <a class="btn primary" href="https://wa.me/6281266895655" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Chat via WhatsApp</a>
  </div>
</section>

<footer id="contact">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="footer-grid">
      <div>
        <div class="footer-brand">
          <img src="data:image/jpeg;base64,/9j/4AAQSkZJRgABAQAAAQABAAD/2wCEAAYGBgYHBgcICAcKCwoLCg8ODAwODxYQERAREBYiFRkVFRkVIh4kHhweJB42KiYmKjY+NDI0PkxERExfWl98fKcBBgYGBgcGBwgIBwoLCgsKDw4MDA4PFhAREBEQF[...]
          <span>NATERRA</span>
        </div>
        <p>Small Choice, Big Impact. Tisu ramah lingkungan untuk kebutuhan harianmu.</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h4>Jelajahi</h4>
        <ul>
          <li><a href="#about">Tentang Kami</a></li>
          <li><a href="#products">Produk</a></li>
          <li><a href="#values">Kenapa Kami</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h4>Kontak</h4>
        <ul>
          <li>griffinsandyyyy@gmail.com</li>
          <li>0812-6689-5655</li>
          <li>Medan, Indonesia</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="footer-bottom">
      <span>© 2026 Naterra. Semua hak dilindungi.</span>
      <span>Small Choice, Big Impact</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>

<script>
  const revealEls = document.querySelectorAll('[data-reveal]');
  const obs = new IntersectionObserver((entries)=>{
    entries.forEach(e=>{ if(e.isIntersecting){ e.target.classList.add('in'); obs.unobserve(e.target); } });
  },{threshold:0.15});
  revealEls.forEach(el=>obs.observe(el));
</script>

</body>
</html>